      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a showroom-fresh experience. This vehicle is in impeccable condition, featuring a deep obsidian metallic finish that retains a glass-like luster, completely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. The interior is a sanctuary of hand-stitched leather that remains supple and pristine, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every surface, from the brushed aluminum accents to the panoramic glass roof, has been meticulously maintained. Mechanically, the car performs flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and a recent 150-point inspection. This is a rare, collector-grade example that has been strictly garaged and pampered since day one, offering the premium technology package and unparalleled reliability for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
